import React from 'react'
import Header from './Header'
import Hero from './Hero'
import Client from './Client'
import About from './About'
import Stats from './Stats'
import Section from './Section'

function Index() {
  return (
    <>
    <Header></Header>
    <Hero></Hero>
    <Client></Client>
    <About></About>
    <Stats></Stats>
    <Section></Section>
    </>
  )
}

export default Index
